'''司徒宇斌'''（{{lang-en|Sitoh Yih Pin}}，{{bd|1963年|12月2日||}}），新加坡政治人物，[[人民行动党|人民行动党]]党员。他是{{tsl|en|Potong Pasir Single Member Constituency|波东巴西单选区}}的[[国会议员|国会议员]]<ref>http://www.elections.gov.sg/gazette%5CG_ParE2011%5C2011-05-09%20Candidates%20declared%20to%20have%20been%20elected.pdf#zoom=100 {{Wayback|url=http://www.elections.gov.sg/gazette%5CG_ParE2011%5C2011-05-09%20Candidates%20declared%20to%20have%20been%20elected.pdf#zoom=100 |date=20110624005440 }} ''Singapore Election Department : Gazette Notification on Candidates declared to have been elected Members of Parliament (2011)''</ref>，同时是新加坡会计公司Nexia TS公共会计公司的主席<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=7767305&privcapId=7767377|title=Yih Pin Sitoh: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg|website=www.bloomberg.com|access-date=2017-09-11|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911211425/https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=7767305&privcapId=7767377|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 会计生涯 ==
1987年，司徒宇斌凭会计学士学位毕业于[[新加坡国立大学|新加坡国立大学]]，是新加坡和澳大利亚的注册{{le|特许会计师|Charted accountant}}，曾任[[毕马威|毕马威]]审计经理，之后于1993年创办Nexia TS公共会计公司（{{lang|en|Nexia TS Public Accounting}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nexiats.com.sg/index.php?page=about-us|title=Nexia TS - About Us|website=www.nexiats.com.sg|access-date=2017-09-11|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911210151/http://www.nexiats.com.sg/index.php?page=about-us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 政治生涯 ==
司徒宇斌于[[2001年新加坡大选|2001年]]首次踏足政界，代表[[人民行动党|人民行动党]]挑战自1984年起一直担任波东巴西单选区议员的[[詹时中|詹时中]]，最终以47.6%的得票数告负<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.singapore-elections.com/candidates-s.html |title=Archived copy |access-date=2011-03-22 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110501040252/http://www.singapore-elections.com/candidates-s.html |archive-date=2011-05-01 |website=Singapore Election Candidates }}</ref>。[[2006年新加坡大選|2006年]]，他再度挑战詹时中，又以44.2%的票数告负。到了[[2011年新加坡大选|2011年]]，服务波东巴西选区27年的詹时中转战[[碧山-大巴窑集选区|碧山-大巴窑集选区]]，但失败，而司徒宇斌的对手变成了詹时中的妻子{{le|罗文丽|Lina Chiam}}。两人的对决是2011年选战中结果最近的一场，司徒以114张票50.36%的投票率胜出<ref>http://www.elections.gov.sg/elections_results2011.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.elections.gov.sg/elections_results2011.html |date=20110513155116 }} ''Singapore Elections Department : 2011 PARLIAMENTARY GENERAL ELECTION RESULTS''</ref>。2011年5月9日，司徒正式出任国会议员。[[2015年新加坡大选|2015年大选]]中，他成功留任<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lee|first1=Min Kok|title=GE2015: PAP's Sitoh Yih Pin retains Potong Pasir SMC with 66.4 per cent of votes|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/politics/ge2015-paps-sitoh-yih-pin-retains-potong-pasir-smc-with-664-per-cent-of-votes|accessdate=2017-09-11|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-12|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911205033/http://www.straitstimes.com/politics/ge2015-paps-sitoh-yih-pin-retains-potong-pasir-smc-with-664-per-cent-of-votes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年1月，司徒入选{{le|人民行动党中央执行委员会|Central Executive Committee (PAP)}}<ref>{{cite news|title=4 new members co-opted into PAP's Central Executive Committee Read|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/4-new-members-co-opted-into-pap-s-central-executive-committee-7534868|accessdate=2017-09-11|publisher=Channel NewsAsia|date=2017-01-05|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911205104/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/4-new-members-co-opted-into-pap-s-central-executive-committee-7534868|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

司徒宇斌目前担任波东巴西市镇会主席及波东巴西草根组织顾问<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.talkmed.com.sg/board-member/mr-sitoh-yih-pin/|title=Mr Sitoh Yih Pin - TalkMED Group Ltd|work=TalkMED Group Ltd|access-date=2017-09-11|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911193640/http://www.talkmed.com.sg/board-member/mr-sitoh-yih-pin/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是人民行动党社群基金会执行成员<ref>{{cite web|title=PCF COUNCIL|url=http://www.pcf.org.sg/About-Us/Our-Structure/PCF-Council/Organisation|accessdate=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911162454/http://www.pcf.org.sg/About-Us/Our-Structure/PCF-Council/Organisation|archive-date=2017-09-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 其他职务 ==
